view.definition:
SELECT deals.uuid,
    deals.car,
    x15_mask_sensitive_data(deals.customer) AS customer,
    deals.location,
    deals.dealer,
    deals.journey_type,
    deals.status,
    deals.brand,
    deals.country,
    deals.region,
    deals.language,
    deals.created_at,
    deals.updated_at,
    deals.appointment,
    deals.currency,
    deals.finance,
    deals.attributes,
    deals.second_language_data,
    deals.user_id,
    x15_mask_sensitive_data(deals.insurance) AS insurance,
    deals.deleted_at,
    deals.expressions_of_interest,
    deals.export_count,
    deals.quote_uuid
   FROM deals;
view.name: deals_masked

view.definition:
SELECT (jsonb_set(((failed_messages.body)::jsonb -> 'deal'::text), '{customer}'::text[], '"****"'::jsonb))::text AS body,
    failed_messages.headers,
    failed_messages.queue_name,
    failed_messages.created_at,
    failed_messages.available_at,
    failed_messages.delivered_at
   FROM failed_messages;
view.name: failed_messages_masked

view.definition:
SELECT finance_applications.code,
    finance_applications.submission_id,
    finance_applications.status,
    x15_mask_sensitive_data(finance_applications.customer_details) AS customer_details,
    finance_applications.finance,
    finance_applications.attributes,
    finance_applications.created_at,
    finance_applications.updated_at,
    finance_applications.region,
    finance_applications.country,
    finance_applications.brand
   FROM finance_applications;
view.name: finance_applications_masked

view.definition:
SELECT pg_stat_statements.userid,
    pg_stat_statements.dbid,
    pg_stat_statements.toplevel,
    pg_stat_statements.queryid,
    pg_stat_statements.query,
    pg_stat_statements.plans,
    pg_stat_statements.total_plan_time,
    pg_stat_statements.min_plan_time,
    pg_stat_statements.max_plan_time,
    pg_stat_statements.mean_plan_time,
    pg_stat_statements.stddev_plan_time,
    pg_stat_statements.calls,
    pg_stat_statements.total_exec_time,
    pg_stat_statements.min_exec_time,
    pg_stat_statements.max_exec_time,
    pg_stat_statements.mean_exec_time,
    pg_stat_statements.stddev_exec_time,
    pg_stat_statements.rows,
    pg_stat_statements.shared_blks_hit,
    pg_stat_statements.shared_blks_read,
    pg_stat_statements.shared_blks_dirtied,
    pg_stat_statements.shared_blks_written,
    pg_stat_statements.local_blks_hit,
    pg_stat_statements.local_blks_read,
    pg_stat_statements.local_blks_dirtied,
    pg_stat_statements.local_blks_written,
    pg_stat_statements.temp_blks_read,
    pg_stat_statements.temp_blks_written,
    pg_stat_statements.blk_read_time,
    pg_stat_statements.blk_write_time,
    pg_stat_statements.wal_records,
    pg_stat_statements.wal_fpi,
    pg_stat_statements.wal_bytes
   FROM pg_stat_statements(true) pg_stat_statements(userid, dbid, toplevel, queryid, query, plans, total_plan_time, min_plan_time, max_plan_time, mean_plan_time, stddev_plan_time, calls, total_exec_time, min_exec_time, max_exec_time, mean_exec_time, stddev_exec_time, rows, shared_blks_hit, shared_blks_read, shared_blks_dirtied, shared_blks_written, local_blks_hit, local_blks_read, local_blks_dirtied, local_blks_written, temp_blks_read, temp_blks_written, blk_read_time, blk_write_time, wal_records, wal_fpi, wal_bytes);
view.name: pg_stat_statements
pg_stat_statements_info

view.definition:
SELECT users.id,
    regexp_replace((users.email)::text, '^(.).*(.)@'::text, '\1****\2@'::text) AS email,
    x15_mask_sensitive_data(users.data) AS data,
    users.brand,
    users.country,
    users.region
   FROM users;
view.name: users_masked
